{"tid":1566840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中秋節快樂啊！各位！","createTime":"2019-09-13T18:46:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T19:58:17.000Z","uid":166273,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"99617cb4a3b21e4e4500980193c82d20773f2bfd","tid":1566840,"uid":166273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:46:53.000Z","msg":"小弟今日夜晚8點由沙田坳開始上獅子山，由山腳到山腰一路都見到好多手足同我地講加油、轉個灣就到、中秋節快樂等等等等。<br />\n<br />\n途中聽到好多人播「願光榮歸香港」、「自游Be water」、「問誰還未發聲」、「肥媽有話兒」，亦好多人一齊跟住唱。<br />\n<br />\n直到10點鐘大家一齊<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">鄭嘉穎式</span>咆哮<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用左三個幾鐘時間終於上到獅子尾，真係好靚好靚，個一刻我係到諗：原來係山上面望落去既香港係咁樣...，我好肯定呢幾個鐘絕對值得！<br />\n<br />\n仲有呀，我地係山頂望到對面海有支雷射筆好撚勁揪，可以照到上嚟呢邊獅子山真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今個中秋真係多謝咁多位手足陪我過，宜家對腳已經冇晒力，聽日可能出唔到嚟，係到道個歉先，希望各位手足可以幫我出多一份力，香港人加油！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">利申返：我係由上山到落山都係到播「中秋節快樂呀！各位！」個位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，亦聽到大家笑一笑，我聽到都好開心</span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">，同埋我第一次行山，落到山對腳已經不停咁震</span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">咁多位，中秋節快樂！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n我願榮光歸香港！</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"f7bda48e933ac077154a209ec653099b25b90c2a","tid":1566840,"uid":166273,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:49:30.000Z","msg":"補返圖比大家，不過我影相唔叻，屌細力D<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">仲要係用手機影<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2TzB35Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2TzB35Y.png&h=46fafcc8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w9iLcZm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw9iLcZm.jpg&h=a51b56da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3q6MGSN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3q6MGSN.png&h=75900e11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30cc802701d183bf6e7a4287234cae5beaac6769","tid":1566840,"uid":166273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:50:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中秋節快樂啊！各位！</span>"},{"pid":"16d5b8fef69ca5dbb60f0850885c3c78afa3ef5e","tid":1566840,"uid":166273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:51:51.000Z","msg":"何以 這土地 淚再流"},{"pid":"3f8617f10ed18dcfcb09d35ffc2fad9a8fab83df","tid":1566840,"uid":166273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16d5b8fef69ca5dbb60f0850885c3c78afa3ef5e","tid":1566840,"uid":166273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:51:51.000Z","msg":"何以 這土地 淚再流"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:52:06.000Z","msg":"何以 令眾人 亦憤恨"},{"pid":"8ee955ef3b9ff2712518f236750efcd2c680d479","tid":1566840,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:52:58.000Z","msg":"仲有十分鐘！ <br />\n<br />\n多謝你安慰我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d177d9b9e5881bd7ced0ec997ee5bc05c9106e91","tid":1566840,"uid":166273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f8617f10ed18dcfcb09d35ffc2fad9a8fab83df","tid":1566840,"uid":166273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16d5b8fef69ca5dbb60f0850885c3c78afa3ef5e","tid":1566840,"uid":166273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:51:51.000Z","msg":"何以 這土地 淚再流"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:52:06.000Z","msg":"何以 令眾人 亦憤恨"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:52:59.000Z","msg":"昴首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透"},{"pid":"c22f48ccf0f1977daed